exportAllData.name: exportAllData
exportAllData.processRule: { contextVar.fileName = 'WorkForce_Efficiency'; contextVar.technicianEfficiencyData = {}; contextVar.technicianEfficiencyCSVData = []; contextVar.headers = ['Work Force', 'Day', 'Task Type', 'No of tasks', 'Planned Minutes', 'Actual Minutes']; if (typeof contextVar.resultArray != 'undefined' && contextVar.resultArray != '') { var len = contextVar.resultArray.length; for (var i = 0; i < len; i++) { contextVar.technicianEfficiencyData['Work Force'] = contextVar.resultArray[i].technicianName; contextVar.technicianEfficiencyData['Day'] = contextVar.resultArray[i].Days; contextVar.technicianEfficiencyData['Task Type'] = contextVar.resultArray[i].taskTypeName; contextVar.technicianEfficiencyData['No of tasks'] = contextVar.resultArray[i].woId; contextVar.technicianEfficiencyData['Planned Minutes'] = contextVar.resultArray[i].plannedDate; contextVar.technicianEfficiencyData['Actual Minutes'] = contextVar.resultArray[i].actual; contextVar.technicianEfficiencyCSVData.push(contextVar.technicianEfficiencyData); contextVar.technicianEfficiencyData = {}; } } }
